Plotting Life Expectancy Over the Years

library(ggplot2) 

ggplot(gapminder_df,aes(x =year, y = lifeExp, group = country, color = continent)) +
  geom_line() +
  scale_y_log10() +
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(1997, 2007)) #get a warning message that you removed data
